data.title: Bronze Star Valor
data.text:
Available to: Recipients of the Bronze Star â€“ Valor

Documentation Required:

For applicants that have been discharged from the armed forces: DD214 form, along with a copy of orders that awarded the medal or a copy of the certificate or citation granting the medal

For applicants who have not been discharged from the armed forces: Copy of orders that awarded the medal or copy of certificate or citation granting the medal

For those who do not have documentation listed above: a written communication from the Department of Veteran Services that certifies the applicant has received the medal or award

Cost: None for first plate. Second plate - $26.50 annual fee (initial fee is $28.15). Subsequent plates - $26.50 annual fee (initial fee is $29.80).

Vehicle Classes: Passenger, Motorcycle
